Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:14.99,Opening-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}niji no you ni ashita wa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:14.99,Opening-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}{\fnCambria\fs36}Uhodila do mostu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:14.99,Opening-Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}虹のように明日は...
